#text=My cousin wanted me to visit him in Florida over the summer and I needed to make a plan and book a flight to get there .
#text=After searching on the internet for a great price , I found one and booked it .
#text=The day of the flight I was a bit nervous as it had been a long time since I had flown on an airplane .
#text=I boarded along with the other passengers and realized that I had a great window seat in a good location so I was n't crowded in .
#text=After a very smooth take off , the flight attendants brought me something to drink and a snack .
#text=It was a very smooth flight and about 6 hours later , I ended up at my destination .
#text=It all went very nicely and I was happy to be back on the ground .
#text=After we parked at our terminal , we all orderly departed the airplane .
#text=After walking down the tunnel leading into the airport , I saw my family members waiting for me .
